Anita Barone https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anita_Barone 0 Anita Louise Barone (born September 25, 1964) is an American actress. She is best known for co-starring roles in sitcoms The Jeff Foxworthy Show, Daddio, Shake It Up and The War at Home. Anita_Louise_Barone ( born September_25_,_1964 ) is an_American_actress .
